{"tid":1927434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嗰班留學撚返香港 又諗住偷偷哋唔自我隔離嘅 我屌晒你哋老母","createTime":"2020-03-15T18:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T10:50:55.000Z","uid":66888,"like":100,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"675b32a7d5a8cb75537ea8cc6fc2e3ac4dd94c17","tid":1927434,"uid":66888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"利申先 我自己喺英國讀緊，一定會隔離<br />\n<br />\n發覺身邊有唔少香港人諗住返嚟又唔打算自我隔離，諗住偷偷哋冇人知。 尢其是嗰班平時得把口，文宣都冇點po 過嘅偽黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 自私到一個點，根本真係愛香港，有小小公德心嘅都會自動自覺隔離。直接同佢哋講就一大堆藉口話冇咁易中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嚟緊幾個星期起碼成萬人喺歐美加返嚟，如果一成人偷走嘅話都肯定爆到七彩 仲未計嗰班用香港做逃生門嘅支那人，佢哋一定唔會自我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留學生見到依個po 嘅話可唔可以乖乖哋隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔想香港因為我哋搞到大爆發呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b51f6a225d5202f6bde227d2d1984a4d5a64d2","tid":1927434,"uid":66888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def8bd02d8542c81e7c5db6db75b36b54f57680e","tid":1927434,"uid":66888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31d206f96c8cad4e581a3d912426846b5633d88","tid":1927434,"uid":66888,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T19:07:46.000Z","msg":"高質黃channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sIRVSsT8DXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsIRVSsT8DXc&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=4ea251b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sIRVSsT8DXc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w04mlzFgq18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw04mlzFgq18&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bv